{"tid":1668382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］有冇人今朝係黨鐵執到一個藍色既散紙包..（內有藥）","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T12:19:32.000Z","uid":82828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee47714442c9c96b3bcf3246e3a34afb8740f908","tid":1668382,"uid":82828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝9:30鑽石山入閘，經旺角、金鐘轉車，大約10:00銅鑼灣出閘時發現成個散紙包唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裏面有兩張八達通（自動增果張已報失）、幾蚊散紙、一疊我本人既卡片，仲有最重要既藥！！<br />\n<br />\n連登有愛 可唔可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n散紙包示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihwqS2w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FihwqS2w.gif&h=d118e414&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f51b107caa2a035a614efa2b0285f420d2bb5d3","tid":1668382,"uid":210683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca7744834475cf5c6e0b6889714a3eeba9d40f5","tid":1668382,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏同我入嚟<br />\n想connect全世界同我入嚟<br />\n把握時機 食住個勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1bd99387a1dc24896c916a29b0dd7a11aed8387","tid":1668382,"uid":202921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"41316b8b3b2051ca